1. *Oficir* je veoma odgovoran za živote vojnika. (*Officer* is very responsible for the lives of soldiers.)

2. *Oficira* sam sreo na ulici juče. (*I met an officer* on the street yesterday.)

3. Vojnici su bili impresionirani *oficirovim* hrabrosti. (The soldiers were impressed by the *officer's* bravery.)

4. Da bi postao *oficir*, moraš proći kroz posebnu obuku. (To become an *officer*, you have to go through special training.)

5. *Oficiri* u našoj vojsci dobijaju visoke plate. (*Officers* in our army receive high salaries.)

6. Najmlađi *oficir* u jedinici je bio veoma sposoban. (The youngest *officer* in the unit was very capable.)

7. Ovo je kancelarija *oficira* koji je zadužen za obuku. (This is the office of the *officer* in charge of training.)

8. Zaduženja *oficira* su vrlo raznolika. (*Officer's duties* are very diverse.)

9. Bilo je nekoliko *oficira* na ceremoniji dodele nagrada. (There were several *officers* at the award ceremony.)

10. *Oficiri* su bili vrlo strogi prema regrutima tokom obuke. (*Officers* were very strict with recruits during training.)